{"tid":2265373,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一件小學做過最好笑嘅事","createTime":"2020-10-31T11:20:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-01T11:58:34.000Z","uid":168414,"like":31,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"8df6e53806d31b2ff69e888d697c53db1a524528","tid":2265373,"uid":168414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T11:20:49.000Z","msg":"突然諗返起<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n小學某年聯歡會嘅前一晚<br />\n我食晚飯個陣諗起d 好on9既嘢<br />\n就係放d食剩嘅雞翼骨落一個空嘅薯片叔叔筒入面<br />\n等聯歡會嗰陣請其他同學食<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁個晚我都唔記得放左幾多舊雞翼骨入去<br />\n之後搵蓋冚住個筒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n第二朝早起身<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一打開個蓋聞下<br />\n哇屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />臭撚到仆街 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />差d嘔左岀黎<br />\n(exactly係垃圾車個浸味)<br />\n我就咁帶住筒垃圾車返去聯歡會<br />\n咁小學聯歡會就梗係不停R人野食啦<br />\n食人野之餘我又會係咁問人食唔食薯片呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一話食我就會打開筒野比佢地聞下<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢地d反應令到我嗰日拎住筒野玩得好開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而家諗返起覺得好撚好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n小學記得我既勿相認<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fee27d303dbb43f2ca86a4104089d1ec5105e0d","tid":2265373,"uid":191815,"like":18,"dislike":2,"score":16,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T11:22:17.000Z","msg":"屙尿 鬥高鬥大力<br />\n啲尿射向流水牆再反彈 全排人彈到成臉都係"},{"pid":"6abd9f87477c714c136d7002229ec43e15f2e922","tid":2265373,"uid":343268,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T11:25:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除